        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "00:06.500",
        "end": "00:14.500",
        "original": "たくさんの人たちと、その人たちが発する熱気に包まれて、私はすごくワクワクしてた",
        "english": "Surrounded by so many people and the heat they emitted, I was really excited.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "00:15.500",
        "end": "00:18.500",
        "original": "別だかすごく懐かしい感じがした……",
        "english": "It felt somehow very nostalgic...",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "00:20.800",
        "end": "00:23.500",
        "original": "ねえねえ、キミ、大丈夫？",
