        "original": "あ、うちはミオだよ。占い師をやってる",
        "english": "Oh, I'm Mio. I'm a fortune teller.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "00:31.800",
        "end": "00:36.500",
        "original": "ん、キミ、何かを探してるね。そう占いにでてる",
        "english": "Hmm, you're looking for something. That's what the fortune says.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "00:36.800",
        "end": "00:38.200",
        "original": "わかるの？",
        "english": "You can tell?",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "00:38.500",
        "end": "00:43.500",
        "original": "うん、よかったら話してみて、何か力になれるかもしれないし",
        "english": "Yeah, if you'd like, try talking to me. I might be able to help.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "00:44.000",
        "end": "00:45.500",
        "original": "実は……",
        "english": "Actually...",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "00:48.500",
        "end": "00:52.000",
        "original": "なるほど……キミは『オンガク』を探してるんだね",
        "english": "I see... You're looking for \"Music\".",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "00:53.000",
