        "original": "それならあそこに行ってみればいいんじゃない？",
        "english": "In that case, why don't you try going over there?",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "00:56.500",
        "end": "01:00.500",
        "original": "世界の果てにあるっていう、光の塔",
