        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "01:06.000",
        "end": "01:11.500",
        "original": "だからそこに行ってお願いをすれば、キミの探しものも見つかるんじゃないかな",
        "english": "So if you go there and make a wish, maybe you'll find what you're looking for.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "01:12.000",
